{"tid":1538410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"魯比奧：美在港問題上有很多選項","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10a7ad139fdca31114bb625a04044fc324280171","tid":1538410,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"反對《逃犯條例》修訂示威引起國際關注。美國共和黨參議員魯比奧(Marco Rubio)在《華盛頓郵報》撰文，指華盛頓政府應該向中方表明，美方在香港問題上，並非只有終止香港特別關稅區地位的「核選項」，尚有其他靈活及強力回應。<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧又稱，其他方法包括引用「天安門制裁」，對與黑社會合作、引發暴力及虐待扣留人士的本港警務人員，實施制裁，又或引用《馬格尼茨基法案》，制裁嚴重侵犯人權的官員。<br />\n<br />\n同時，美國國會應通過《香港人權與民主法案》，制裁削弱香港自治的本港及內地官員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2241564/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2241564%2F&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=e8564819\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2241564/</a>"},{"pid":"337103bfd6ab3c506be77f47335e69b6a7265dd4","tid":1538410,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f387947c768e2f12ae518409f4b7c7ed79f142e","tid":1538410,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"想收貨嘅，睇下呢個名單：<br />\n<br />\n熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019"},{"pid":"960e23eed46ed935877e6a8f37cfd80682c682ca","tid":1538410,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcMrUP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.